| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2658 — Recovery Inhibition (donutleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2f0eb341-0270-5c42-8720-2ccce4d36002"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
